_:N0d056bcc362041ab8b3062497b8e3437 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Heidi Alexander MP was appointed as the Secretary of State for Transport on 29 November 2024.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously the Minister of State at the Ministry of Justice from the 8 July 2024 to 29 November 2024. She was elected as the MP for Swindon South in July 2024.</p>\n" .
